# name: test_command_help_matches_snapshot[setup_install]
  '''
  
   Usage: assembly setup install [OPTIONS]
  
   Set up your coding agent for AssemblyAI (docs MCP server + skills).
  
   Installs three things: the assemblyai-docs MCP server (live API docs, via
   `claude mcp add`), the AssemblyAI skill (via `npx skills add`), and the
   bundled
   aai-cli skill (copied from this package, no network). Each step is idempotent
   and skipped if already present unless --force.
  
  ╭─ Options ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
  │ --scope          [user|project|local]  Config scope to register the MCP      │
  │                                        under. Presence is detected across    │
  │                                        all scopes.                           │
  │                                        [default: user]                       │
  │ --force                                Reinstall even if already present.    │
  │ --json   -j                            Output raw JSON.                      │
  │ --help                                 Show this message and exit.           │
  ╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯
  
   Examples
   Set up your coding agent for AssemblyAI
   $ assembly setup install
   Install for the current project only
   $ assembly setup install --scope project
   Reinstall everything even if already present
   $ assembly setup install --force
  
  
  
  '''
# ---
# name: test_command_help_matches_snapshot[setup_remove]
  '''
  
   Usage: assembly setup remove [OPTIONS]
  
   Remove the AssemblyAI MCP server and skills from your coding agent.
  
  ╭─ Options ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
  │ --scope          [user|project|local]  Only remove the MCP from this scope.  │
  │                                        Default: remove from whichever scope  │
  │                                        it exists in.                         │
  │ --json   -j                            Output raw JSON.                      │
  │ --help                                 Show this message and exit.           │
  ╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯
  
   Examples
   Remove the AssemblyAI MCP server and skills
   $ assembly setup remove
   Remove only from the project scope
   $ assembly setup remove --scope project
  
  
  
  '''
# ---
